name: heart of the ocean
description: donyoku's mother let him go behind the sea when he was new born ...uminochichi (ocean's father) found him and took him to the depths of the ocean Inside a glass bubble in which the heart of the ocean was, he raises him.. When he reached the age of 18 He understood the story of his life, betrayed his father and stole the heart of the ocean... uminochichi was angry, but he could not do anything without the heart of the ocean...People say that every time the sea becomes a storm, it's uminochichi who calls donyoku with groan
